h2. Who is paying for the site?

p. Currently the site is being supported by Peter Mahnke, but over time, I hope that donations and advertising help offset some of the costs.  If you are interested in donating time or money or interested in advertising, please <a href="mailto:support@stmgrts.org.uk">contact us</a>.